Things You Will Need In Your Environment
========================================

0. git - distributed version control
1. cmake - cross platform make
2. make - GNU make
3. googletest - http://code.google.com/p/googletest/ 
4. googlemock - http://code.google.com/p/googlemock/
5. Boost C++ library



Steps To Verify Your Environment:
================================

1. Clone this github repo using the following command

  git clone git://github.com/sriki77/cpp_env_check.git

2. Go into the directory "cpp_env_check"

3. Generate the make files using the command

  cmake .

4. Run the make files

  make clean
  make

5. Run the tests

  make test

6. Run the coverage

  make lcov
============================X===========================	
